        {
          "topic": "Prime Day Performance",
          "content": "We held our biggest Prime Day event ever, with Prime members purchasing over 375 million items worldwide and saving more than $2.5 billion."
        },
        {
          "topic": "Consumer Spending Behavior",
          "content": "Customers remain cautious about pricing, trading down where possible, and seeking deals, particularly in everyday essentials and personal care categories."
        },
        {
          "topic": "Delivery Speeds",
          "content": "We set another record for delivery speed, delivering the fastest speeds ever in the United States for the year-to-date period through Q3."
